鹅公湾是大鹏半岛西部一个罕见的海湾。海滩背倚群山，面朝大海。在海滩后面，有一个银色的瀑布，从山涧流下，流向蔚蓝的大海。\n鹅公湾是一个人烟稀少、无污染的海滩。目前这里被开辟为养殖场，无法直接进入。户外穿越到达的方式有三种。第一种最近的是从柚柑湾沿着海岸线徒步穿越到鹅公湾，距离大约1公里。第二种是从北面洋畴湾方向海岸线穿越过来，距离更长。第三种是从去鹅公湾的公路上的溯溪路线溪降到达。三种路线均有一定难度，请判断自己能力酌情前往。\n#户外 #户外徒步 #深圳 #沙滩 #深圳周末去哪儿 #小众旅行地 #深圳周末去哪儿 #深圳海边 #深圳旅行 #深圳周末做什么 #徒步 #徒步路线推荐 ","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/chg","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 782)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 1864 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":4,"text":"04-13 上海","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eil","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 35)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 2688 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":5,"text":"共 17条评论","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh1","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 189, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 2820 - 230, 2400)"},{"index":6,"resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/bx","class":"android.widget.RelativeLayout","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 143)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 2875 - 1080, 2400)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"爱评论的人运气都不差~","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh2","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":tr